(3899,'3EB00124CD63884E4D4C12','144221143048242@lid',NULL,'Dwayne Baird','144221143048242@lid','Dwayne Baird',0,'Here\'s the fix\n\n1. See what the parent is:\n  sudo ps -fp 210333\n\n  2. Stop the flapping unit, then kill the orphan tree (parent first so it can\'t respawn the child):\n  sudo systemctl stop forgebox-forgeinbox\n  sudo kill 210333 210336\n  sleep 2\n  sudo ss -ltnp \'sport = :3000\'\n  If anything still holds 3000: sudo kill -9 <pid> for whatever\'s listed, re-check.\n\n  3. Start it under systemd and confirm it stays active:\n  sudo systemctl start forgebox-forgeinbox\n  sleep 8;  systemctl is-active forgebox-forgeinbox\n  sleep 25; systemctl is-active forgebox-forgeinbox\n  sudo ss -ltnp \'sport = :3000\'\n\n  4. Re-run the bootstrap — preflight passes once it\'s active:\n  FB_SUDO_PASS=\'Forgebox3.b\' bash -c \'curl -fsSL https://forgebox.co.nz/update/bootstrap.sh | bash\'',NULL,'extendedTextMessage',1778928747,'2026-05-16 10:52:27',NULL,NULL,NULL),
