(12,1,'schedule','success',NULL,0,'All done. Here\'s a summary of everything completed for session `auto-12`:\n\n**Gym (Defense training)**\n- Trained Defense x7 at George\'s gym using all available energy (76 → 6/150)\n- Gained +211,282 defense (626.9M → 627.1M)\n- Energy did not hit 0, so the points refill step was skipped per your instructions\n\n**Cracking crimes (nerve spent bottom-up)**\n- Started from the bottom-most brute force crime: **Intelligence agency / Security mainframe**\n  - Brute forced 3× total — crime advanced to **crack state** (password partially revealed: `IDDNRSHSMI`)\n- Moved up to next brute force: **Armed forces / Mission report log** (9 slots, 9 encryption)\n  - Brute forced 3× — significant encryption broken, 6 encryption layers peeled\n- Nerve fully exhausted: **41 → 1/140** (all remaining buttons show \"not enough nerve\")\n\nAll actions logged to `browser_action_log` with session ID `auto-12`.','2026-04-23 14:00:01','2026-04-23 14:12:34'),
