(1806,'3A27AE6A12CFE6583791','180466003009650@lid',NULL,'Shav','180466003009650@lid','Shav',0,'Hey mate, just heard through the grape vine that Carriss is going to get rid of posforge and replace it with square.\n\nShe seems to think the system is lacking a lot of components/inventory that allow her to see and work out how many drinks she’s making and what ingredients are being used. \n\nShe apparently is finding the system is confusing to operate and while it does have potential it’s doesn’t do what she needs it to do. \n\nNow this is third party information so it will be better if you ask her directly what her issues are, but what worked for Regan for a long time isn’t working for her and the way she wants to run the business. \n\nIs it possible, to go in and discuss with her what she needs and give her more training in using the system? Because yeah, it’s pretty serious if she’s looking to pull the plug',NULL,'conversation',1777420044,'2026-04-28 23:47:24',NULL,NULL,NULL),
