(1808,'AC53B50EF91512394906670F95FBFA71','120363031163330338@g.us',NULL,'Jonny Welch','195549894570056@lid','Jonny Welch',0,'G\'day All,\n\nUpdates for upcoming Working Bees. \n\n- Missed on calendar, but end of month Friday mini working will be this Fri 1st May 9am-12pm\n- We will have prep equipment and planting lawn edge garden beds for Friday 8th May (for those who would like to help but can\'t make Saturday 9th May)\n- The above will continue for the Saturday 9th May, plus any other Main Hall, external jobs, as Atrium will be setup for the now mothers lunch.\n\nProvisions for Saturday are simplified late morning tea in place of lunch, approx 11am.\n\nMany thanks, and appreciate all time donated as we know it\'s very busy times for all.\n\nGod Bless\nJonny',NULL,'senderKeyDistributionMessage',1777420753,'2026-04-28 23:59:13',NULL,NULL,NULL),
