(1812,'3A30648325AD0EAE3AEC','180466003009650@lid',NULL,'Shav','180466003009650@lid','Shav',0,'Totally understand. This info I got from Drew at stay grounded. \n\nI know he’s very sceptical on our system and would’ve likely placed a potential negative light on something he doesn’t really know in intimate detail. So I hazard a guess there. Just go in knowing where that info is coming from. \n\nDrew is a mate of mine but yeah, he doesn’t know I’ve invested and I don’t want him to know. That said, he’s not going to promote something he doesn’t use and isn’t invested in.\n\nI suspect carriss just hasn’t been taught how to use our system properly and if she isn’t aware there are systems already in place (if there are) to operate the business the way she wants it’s unlikely she’ll look at the system favourably.',NULL,'conversation',1777421772,'2026-04-29 00:16:13',NULL,NULL,NULL),
