(4508,'3EB03D305681EC8861310B','120363346032343642@g.us',NULL,'Dwayne Baird','144221143048242@lid','Dwayne Baird',0,'Give it this command:\nPer-machine checks (run on each clone)\n\n  # 1. Kernel hostname MUST be \'forgebox\' (not the box name) — else the\n  #    watchdog\'s getent forgebox.local fails and restarts avahi every ~90s\n  hostname                       # → forgebox\n  cat /etc/hostname              # → forgebox\n\n  # 2. avahi mDNS name MUST be unique per box\n  grep -E \'^\\s*host-name|use-ipv6\' /etc/avahi/avahi-daemon.conf\n  #    → host-name=<thisbox>   (toby / orion / …), all different\n\n  # 3. Dashboard alias unique (cosmetic but should match the box)\n  grep hostname_alias /opt/forgebox/system/instance.json\n\n  # 4. IPv6 link-local — THE clone-collision check.\n  ip -6 addr show scope link | grep inet6\n  #    Record the fe80::… on each box.\n\n  # 5. Watchdog isn\'t churning avahi\n  journalctl -u avahi-daemon --since \"-2h\" | grep -c \"avahi-daemon .*starting up\"\n  #    → low single digits. Tens/hundreds = restart loop (see §5 of runbook)\n\n  The one cross-machine comparison that matters\n\n  Collect the fe80::… link-local from step 4 on every clone and compare:\n\n  - All different → good, no IPv6 mDNS collision.\n  - Any two identical → that\'s the rolling-dropout cause. On the duplicate(s), regenerate the IPv6 stable-secret and reboot:\n  sudo sysctl -w net.ipv6.conf.all.stable_secret=\"$(uuidgen)\"\n  # persist in /etc/sysctl.d/ then reboot\n\n  Pass criteria (whole fleet)\n\n              Check             │           Must be            \n   Kernel hostname              │ forgebox on every box        \n   avahi host-name=             │ unique per box               \n   instance.json hostname_alias │ unique per box               \n   IPv6 fe80:: link-local       │ unique across all boxes      \n   avahi restarts / 2 h          low single digits, not tens+ \n  The two independent failure modes this catches: shared IPv6 link-local (clones colliding → external <box>.local flaps ~40–60%) and kernel hostname ≠ forgebox (watchdog restart loop → ~10 s mDNS blackouts every ~90 s). A clone is only safe to run alongside its siblings when all\n  five rows pass.',NULL,'conversation',1779185664,'2026-05-19 10:14:25',NULL,NULL,NULL),
